                    <container_2099145685
                        cq:styleIds="[1653545825688,1653545835982]"
                        jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:36.975-05:00"
                        jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                        jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:36.975-05:00"
                        jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                        jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                        sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/container/v2/container">
                        <text
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:55.596-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:06:12.066-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>At AbbVie, we are passionate about developing advanced therapies to help address the world’s greatest health challenges. We also are committed to providing access to therapies that are not yet approved for use to people who are suffering from a serious or life-threatening illness or condition and might potentially benefit from these products.&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>To do that, AbbVie has developed a Pre-Approval Access to Investigational Products Policy. It outlines important considerations we take into account when evaluating a doctor’s request to use investigational products in a patient with a serious or life-threatening illness or condition.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>We created this policy so we can make an appropriate medical decision about access to investigational products as quickly and as appropriately as possible.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_copy
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_copy
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:16.221-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-16T16:35:59.636-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Who this policy covers"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_copy_979714877
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:55.596-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:06:45.996-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>Our policy applies to requests on behalf of individual patients (Single-Patient Access) and to certain groups of patients with similar characteristics (Multi-Patient Protocol Access). A Pre-Approval Access program may also be referred to as Expanded Access, Compassionate Use or Named Patient Basis programs, as defined by local regulations. While our policy outlines the general criteria for consideration, each case is unique and will be considered on an individual basis.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_copy_1095444214
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_copy_358383759
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:16.221-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-16T16:36:07.729-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Why we did this"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_copy_678222437
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:55.596-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-07T16:16:13.842-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>The primary option for patients to get access to investigational products is to participate in a clinical trial. Patients and physicians can learn more by reviewing&amp;nbsp;information on current or planned clinical trials&amp;nbsp;by visiting the &lt;a href=&quot;https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/results?term=abbvie&amp;amp;Search=Search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>U.S. National Institutes of Health website&lt;/a> and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.clinicaltrialsregister.eu/ctr-search/search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>EU Clinical Trials Register website&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>We recognize, there are extraordinary circumstances where access to these investigational products outside of a clinical trial is appropriate. Under our Access to Investigational Products Policy, a patient’s doctor can request consideration for access if three basic criteria are met:&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;ul>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>The patient suffers from a serious or life-threatening illness or condition&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>There are no other suitable treatment options&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;li>The patient does not qualify for ongoing clinical trials&lt;/li>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;/ul>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_copy_1999393922
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_copy_510851033
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:16.221-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-16T16:36:16.102-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Other things we consider"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_copy_1783651565
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:55.596-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:12:54.212-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>Two other important factors play a role in our consideration of each patient request.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The first is to ensure that the potential benefits of the product outweigh the risks to the individual patient. Physicians consider this before they prescribe any therapy for a patient; it’s absolutely vital in these serious cases that an investigational product doesn’t add new or unreasonable risks for a patient.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>The second is to ensure that providing access under this policy doesn’t have a negative impact on clinical trials. Such an impact would potentially delay approval and broad access so that a new drug may be offered to as many patients as possible.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_copy_622187355
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_copy_119817274
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:16.221-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-16T16:36:24.867-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Making a request"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_copy_1291330616
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:55.596-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:14:07.946-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>Requests for access to investigational products under development and prior to approval under this policy must be made by Treating Physicians. Treating Physicians should contact AbbVie via this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://info.abbvie.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>link&lt;/a>. Complete the necessary fields and submit. Following submission, you can expect to receive the necessary forms to begin the request process.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_copy_11014
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_copy_1696500146
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:16.221-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-16T16:36:32.913-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Our commitment"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <text_copy_1146998552
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:36:55.596-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:45:12.247-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                            text="&lt;p>Because we are committed to addressing the world’s greatest health challenges, AbbVie takes requests for access under this policy very seriously. We will treat every request with respect, dignity and in a way that protects the privacy of the patient. We will consider each request carefully, individually and fairly. And once we have all the necessary information, we will strive to provide a decision as soon as we can.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>If you have questions about our policy, please consult the below FAQ.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
                        <separator_copy_1101467000
                            cq:styleIds="[1662756423318]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:01.839-05:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/separator/v2/separator"/>
                        <title_copy_169650014
                            cq:styleIds="[1659545825678,1661545829678,1651545825692]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:37:16.221-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2024-08-16T16:36:42.392-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="VALENSX5"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            jcr:title="Frequently asked questions"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                            type="h2"
                            variant="h"/>
                        <accordion
                            cq:styleIds="[1]"
                            jcr:created="{Date}2023-01-24T17:45:27.129-05:00"
                            jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                            jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-07T16:15:31.367-04:00"
                            jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/accordion/v2/accordion"
                            headingElement="h5"
                            singleExpansion="false">
                            <item_1674600349919
                                cq:panelTitle="What investigational products are available for individual patients?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-07T16:09:41.974-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>In general, only those investigational products that are part of existing or planned clinical trials would be considered for access under this policy. You can consult the U.S. National Institutes of Health for their&amp;nbsp;current list of &lt;a href=&quot;https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/results?term=abbvie&amp;amp;Search=Search&quot;>AbbVie’s clinical trials&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;or other local programs detailing clinical trials such as the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.clinicaltrialsregister.eu/ctr-search/search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>EU Clinical Trials Register website&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>It’s important to understand that there are circumstances in which we would be unable to provide access to some of these investigational products even though they are being studied in clinical trials.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600352734
                                cq:panelTitle="What diseases or conditions qualify for investigational products available through AbbVie’s Pre-Approval Access pathway?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-07T16:07:41.032-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>In general, only conditions for which there is evidence of potential application of an investigational product that is part of existing or planned clinical trials would be considered for access under this policy. &amp;nbsp;Or the use of the requested product may be considered with justification by the product mechanism of action or by published clinical data for the disease or condition.&amp;nbsp; You can consult the U.S. National Institutes of Health for their current list of &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.clinicaltrialsregister.eu/ctr-search/search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>AbbVie’s clinical trials&lt;/a> or other local programs detailing clinical trials, such as the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.clinicaltrialsregister.eu/ctr-search/search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>EU Clinical Trials Register website&lt;/a>.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>It’s important to understand that there are circumstances in which we would be unable to provide access to some of these investigational products even though they are being studied in clinical trials. Such decisions are made on a case-by-case basis.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600355251
                                cq:panelTitle="How do I apply?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:47:30.040-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>We accept requests only from the doctor who is treating you for the disease or condition. Your doctor should review the above information about how to contact us.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600357585
                                cq:panelTitle="If I am approved, how much will it cost me? Will it be covered by my insurance or government programs?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:26:00.979-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>AbbVie provides products at no cost through the Pre-Approval Access pathway. However, there’s no way for us to know if there will be other costs associated with your treatment. It will depend on your insurance and many other factors. The best thing to do is talk to your doctor.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600360049
                                cq:panelTitle="Who reviews requests?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:27:35.307-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>All Pre-Approval Access requests and programs are managed within AbbVie’s research and development team. Only medical personnel can make decisions about these requests and all other AbbVie employees are specifically prohibited from having any involvement in the decision-making process.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600362767
                                cq:panelTitle="How can I check the status of my request?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:28:13.422-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>We will acknowledge receipt of the request from your doctor within two business days. We also will contact your doctor with any additional questions about the request. We are committed to make an appropriate medical decision about access to investigational products as quickly and as fairly as possible and we will notify your doctor as soon as we have reached&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;a decision.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600366540
                                cq:panelTitle="Why was I denied?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:47:57.839-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Your doctor was provided an explanation of our decision. You should discuss this with your doctor. For both medical and privacy reasons, AbbVie does not directly contact patients.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600369417
                                cq:panelTitle="Why did you deny my request when there are other people with the same disease or condition as me who you approved?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-06T23:28:48.273-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>We consider each request individually, and no two requests are identical. In addition, because there are limited supplies of investigational products, there may simply not be enough to meet all the requests we receive.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600372337
                                cq:panelTitle="How can I appeal your decision?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-01-24T17:48:16.243-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>Your physician would need to contact AbbVie to initiate an appeal. All appeals will be reviewed.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                            <item_1674600375089
                                cq:panelTitle="Because clinical trials are the primary means of access to investigational products, I’d like to consider enrolling in one. How do I do that?"
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-07-07T16:06:13.574-04:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="jewitca"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>It’s important to consider the clinical trial option first, because patients who are eligible for an ongoing clinical trial do not qualify for access to investigational products under AbbVie’s policy.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Each clinical trial has its own eligibility criteria, procedures and enrollment process. Please review the information on the current list of &lt;a href=&quot;https://clinicaltrials.gov/ct2/results?term=abbvie&amp;amp;Search=Search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>AbbVie's clinical trials&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;by visiting the U.S. National Institutes of&amp;nbsp; Health website and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.clinicaltrialsregister.eu/ctr-search/search&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>EU Clinical Trials Register website&lt;/a>, and discuss it with your treating physician.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>If you and your doctor identify a clinical trial for which you might qualify, work with your doctor to begin the application process.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
